Package: birtms
Type: Package
Title: Creates and analyses Bayesian IRT models
Version: 0.0.0.9002
Authors@R: person("Simon", "Schaefer", email = "simon.d.schaefer@chemie.hu-berlin.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Helps building IRT model formulae and model data for fitting Bayesian IRT models with brms / RStan.
    Comes with functions for model comparison, model analysis and model description; possibly also with graphical methods.
